* Iron Raptor could feel the hope and love in Prowl, feeling it mix with her 
own with such a force that it was overwelming.
But wonderful at the same time.
Though, as Prowl slid his arms around her she could feel them even more, and 
also discivered that this new bosies senses were much higher then her last 
one.

Iron Raptor looked right back into Prowls eyes as he looked into hers, 
feeling his amazement at all of the emotions they were both feeling 
together. Finding it quite remarkable herself.
But a smile turned the corners of her lips as Prowl said the words that she 
had been waiting for since she had woken up, meeting his lips half way in 
the kiss.
Feeling nothing other then love in Prowls mind, and how good he felt about 
holding her.

Iron Raptor deepened the kiss a bit, feeling just a tad bit out of place 
with the fact that the only thing between her body and Prowls was a thin 
line of white hair.*
